Component Breakdown:
--------------------

1. HERO SECTION (Center Aligned)
   - Team logos (150x150px)
   - Team names
   - Score display (large, bold)
   - VS divider
   - Match status badge
   - Time/Date info

2. STATISTICS PANEL
   - Possession bar chart
   - Shots comparison
   - Corners
   - Fouls
   - Offsides
   - Pass accuracy

3. MATCH EVENTS TIMELINE
   - Chronological event list
   - Icons for goals, cards, substitutions
   - Player names
   - Time stamps

4. LINEUPS
   - Formation diagram (visual)
   - Player list with numbers
   - Substitutes section
   - Player stats on hover

Color Scheme:
-------------
- Primary: #1a1a2e (dark background)
- Secondary: #16213e (card background)
- Accent: #0f3460 (highlights)
- Success: #22c55e (goals, wins)
- Warning: #eab308 (yellow cards)
- Danger: #ef4444 (red cards)
- Text: #ffffff (primary text)
- Text Secondary: #94a3b8 (meta info)

Typography:
-----------
- Headings: Inter Bold, 24-32px
- Body: Inter Regular, 14-16px
- Score: Inter Black, 48px
- Time: Mono, 14px

Responsive Design:
------------------
Desktop: 3-column layout (stats | events | info)
Tablet: 2-column stacked
Mobile: Single column, cards stacked

Animations:
-----------
- Score updates: Pulse effect
- Live indicator: Blinking dot
- Event additions: Slide in from right
- Page transitions: Fade in/out

